asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: Squeaky
description: Things change, people change. I have changed. And I owe it all to my Savior, the Savior of all FLUFkind, FLUFthulu. The bar life was a dead end, and so was my previous life as Wilhelmina S. Burrows. It always felt like I was between the wrong place and my destiny. Now that I've found my home in the Cult of FLUFthulu, my whole perspective and identity have washed away into the maw of the Exalted One. I asked myself a lot if this was crazy, but after The Wreck and the places FLUFs were forced to retreat to... well, we barely bounced back from the brink of extinction anyway. And where was E.A.R.S.. They were sworn to protect the Fluffle, but power corrupts all of us. Just look at Scrooge, and even Dusty, although he is kind of a tool. At least with the Cult of FLUFthulu, I know what I am getting. My new family takes good care of me, and they have my back. We know that evil stirs, and just like you would sip the hair of the dog the day after some heavy drinking, we aim to fight fire with fire. It was Screamin Jay Flufkins who showed me the strength of the Darkness, late one night. He cast some bones that foretold a Great Awakening and told me that I would be crucial in the resurrection of FLUFthulu. Anyway, I like the new me. I have lost myself in the community of other FLUFthuluites. Come chat sometime, I would love to tell you about our Lord and Savior, FLUFthulu. I still make a mean Carrot Martini, but now that I have found FLUFthulu, I can add an extra bit of magic to my Art. HAIL FLUFTHULU

name: Screamin Jay Flufkins
description: Reincarnated as a rabbit, Screamin Jay Flufkins once lived as an eccentric, voodoo infused rock star, raised by the Blackfoot tribe and with a howling voice that chills to the bone. Known for his flamboyant performances, the true nature of his supernatural ability was kept a secret from his audiences, and instead obfuscated via seemingly meaningless spurts of jibberish on stage. However, Screamin Jay was a guru of the occult. The spells he cast were very real, and his inhabitation of a Fluf is walking, talking proof of his skill, dripping with haze drenched mystery. There is much speculation about the occult networks in the Underground, and Flufkins is no stranger to the depth and darkness beneath it all. Rumors of a Fluf demon worshipping cult abound, and their symbols shown in broad daylight. Whispers of a LuciFur walking amongst the Flufs undetected have reached the ends of the Metaverse. The Undead Flufs live in mansions and drive Lambos, but no one bats an ear. Once myths of an ancient entity known as Flufthulu have begun to gain traction in reality. Despite his rank in the Fluffle, it is possible Flufkins himself commands carrot curses, hare hexes, and even the subterranean souls of sacreligious subjects that predate the Fluf by millennia. Undertaker of the Underground, Screamin Jay dreams of a life back in the limelight. His true identity cannot be exposed, or the Fluffle may become suspicious of his origins. As he waits for the battle for the very heart of the Fluffle to manifest, he sometimes mumbles the same supposed nonsense of his predecessor. Is he speaking in tongues, or will he serve the ill will of the Underworld beneath the Underground?

asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

name: Leapus Leporidae
description: Leapus was the youngest child in large working class family.His father had a factory job with long hours  his mother was a devoted housewife.Being the youngest boy, Lepus was the apple of his mothers eye.This favored status meant Leapus had to learn to be quick to avoid getting a beating from his older brothers.The rough treatment by his older brothers also meant that he grew up tough  as he got older he found he could also stand his ground in a fight with his brothers or anyone else who cared to test his mettle.Leapus was a gifted athlete  was a star of the high school track  field team.His talent could have taken him places but Leapus had a few vices that always managed to get the better of him.Leapus once lost a bet to his friend Bugattii Bunny, the loser had to wear a dress  run through the school cafeteria at lunch time. Bugattii thought it was hilarious but Leapus found it to be invigorating.Much to his own surprise, he found he actually liked wearing the dress, it felt liberating for some reason.Now as an adult Leapus can be found drinking  gambling in clubs or bars often wearing a dress  usually in the company of his old friend Bugattii.Patrons of those establishments know not to start any trouble with Lepus, if they know what is good for them.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)
